=head2 new-debugnode

Creates a B<Gnome::Gsk4::RenderNode> that will add debug information about
the given C<$child>.

Adding this node has no visual effect.

=begin code
method new-debugnode ( N-Object() $child, Str $message --> Gnome::Gsk4::DebugNode \)
